message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the sub-category for Sound and Music Computing, which is the most relevant to speech enhancement. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper deals with speech processing, cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the paper proposes an end-to-end model, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as spectrogram processing is a visual representation of sound, and cs.MM (Multimedia) as speech enhancement is a multimedia application.
